      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-06/tech-firms-in-japan-are-scouring-for-talent-amid-labor-shortage</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管日本寻求经济数字化并重振落后的半导体产业，但它仍面临技术领域熟练人力资源的严重短缺。]]></description>
